without your love, i would die<br/><br/>one night a guy and a girl were driving home from the movies, the boy sensed there was something wrong because of the painful silence they shared between them that night, the girl then asked the boy to pull over because she wanted to talk. she told him that her feelings had changed and that they should move on, a silent tear shed down his cheek as he slowly reached into his pocket and passed her a folded note, at that moment a drunken driver was speeding down that very same street. he swerved right into the drivers seat, killing the boy. miraculously, the girl survived. remembering the note, she pulled it out and read it.                                                                                                                                                                                                
<br /><br />&quot;without you'r love, i would die&quot;
